Juan D'Arienzo

Almost complete discography of 1060 recordings by Juan D'Arienzo and CDs containing them.

There are two recordings from 1929 and some between 1958 and 1963 I am missing (at all or in acceptable quality):

  • Amor pagano, Orquesta Juan D'Arienzo con Raquel Notar, Vals, 1929
  • Maíz frito, Orquesta Juan D'Arienzo con Raquel Notar, Ranchera 1929
  • María Celosa, Orquesta Juan D'Arienzo con Jorge Valdéz, Vals, 1958, RCA Victor
  • No me vengas con cuentos, Orquesta Juan D'Arienzo con Mario Bustos, Tango, 1959, RCA Victor
  • Y no puedo comprender Orquesta Juan D'Arienzo con Mario Bustos, Tango, 1959, RCA-Victor
  • Adiós mi vida, adiós, Orquesta Juan D'Arienzo con Jorge Valdéz, Tango, 1961
  • Tony de Circo, Orquesta Juan D'Arienzo con Jorge Valdéz, Tango, 1962, RCA Victor
  • Los hombres no lloran, Orquesta Juan D'Arienzo con Horacio Palma, Tango, 1962, RCA Victor
  • Olvidemos todo, Orquesta Juan D'Arienzo con Jorge Valdéz, Tango, 1963, RCA Victor

And again one difficult to identify:

  • Con alma de tango, Orquesta Juan D'Arienzo, Tango, 11/1959, RCA Victor (NOT 10/1959)

In case you found missing or wrong information, or you might be able to help finding missing tracks - any feedback is very much welcomed! Please get in contact with me.

If you are interested in one of the CDs mentioned please visit my CD-shop. There are outstanding Juan D'Arienzo CDs by the japanese labels Audio Park and Club Tango Argentino.

Please find more information about Juan D'Arienzo at Todotango.com and at Tangoteca by Johan.
